      Subinterfaces of BA in it.polimi.automata 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      interface  IBA<LABEL extends Label,STATE extends State,TRANSITION extends Transition<LABEL>>
      Represents an Incomplete Buchi Automaton which extends a Buchi automaton with transparent states
      interface  IntersectionBA<LABEL extends Label,STATE extends State,TRANSITION extends Transition<LABEL>>
      Represents a the Intersection of a Buchi Automaton and an Incomplete Buchi automaton
      The state of the automaton must must implement the State interface
      The transition of the automaton must must implement the Transition interface
      The label of the transition must implement the label interface and depending on whether the automaton represents the model or the claim it is a set of proposition or a propositional logic formula

      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  BAImpl<LABEL extends Label,STATE extends StateImpl,TRANSITION extends TransitionImpl<LABEL>>
      Represents a Buchi Automaton, implements the BA interface
      The state of the automaton must must implement the State interface
      The transition of the automaton must must implement the Transition interface
      The label of the transition must implement the label interface and depending on whether the automaton represents the model or the claim it is a set of proposition or a propositional logic formula

      class  IntBAImpl<LABEL extends Label,STATE extends StateImpl,TRANSITION extends TransitionImpl<LABEL>>
